      "widgets_values": [
        "A massive low-frequency detonation tears through the air with a deep concussive boom that rattles into a rolling shockwave rumble, immediately followed by the sharp cracking splinter of concrete and twisted metal shrieking as structures collapse in cascading waves, debris raining down in a chaotic scatter of thuds and clangs and shattering glass. Panicked screaming erupts from multiple directions — a woman shrieking close and to the left, a man yelling something unintelligible further back, children crying in overlapping waves — as a second explosion punches through deeper and heavier than the first, sending a pressure wave that momentarily muffles everything into a dull ringing tinnitus whine before the chaos floods back in. Car alarms blare in staggered rhythms, a fire crackles and roars as it climbs through wreckage, sirens wail in the far distance growing closer, loose metal groans and gives way with a long screeching crash, and running footsteps pound across grit and broken glass in frantic uneven patterns as people flee in every direction beneath the thick haze of settling dust and smoke."
      ],
